  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.10">
<l>āṇallaṉ peṇalla ṉallā valiyumallaṉ</l>
<l>kāṇalu mākā ṉuḷaṉalla ṉillaiyallaṉ</l>
<l>pēṇuṅkāl pēṇu muruvāku mallaṉumāṅ</l>
<l>kōṇai peritu ṭaittem pemmāṉaik kūṟutalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is not man, he is not woman, besides, he is no man-woman.</l>
<l>And he is impossible to see, he is not someone who is, he is not not.</l>
<l>When one thinks [about him] he is the form one thinks and he is not.</l>
<l>There is a big problem in talking about our lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
